parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy incorrectly or not at all, which can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbag warning light is illuminated
airbags do not deploy in an accident
metal shrapnel is released from the airbag
passenger airbag warning sensor is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting and disintegration of the dashboard can cause a sticky and shiny surface, which can reflect sunlight and blind the driver, leading to accidents. Additionally, the melted dashboard can be uncleanable and unsightly.
symptoms: The dashboard is sticky and shiny
the dashboard is melting and disintegrating
the dashboard reflects sunlight and blinds the driver.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing recalled vehicles can leave drivers and passengers at risk of serious injuries or fatalities due to the faulty airbag system.
symptoms: The repair parts are unavailable
the manufacturer has exceeded a reasonable amount of time for the recall repair
the dealer is unable to repair the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion and failure of the subframe can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Abnormal sounds
vehicle veering to one side
difficulty controlling the vehicle
rust or corrosion on the subframe
cracks or breaks in the subframe.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting of the dashboard can cause glare, obstructed visibility, and difficulty driving, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Sticky or melted dashboard
glare on the windshield
difficulty seeing while driving
strong chemical or rubbery smell.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The chipping and corrosion of the paint can lead to rust and damage to the vehicle's body, which can affect its overall safety and performance.
symptoms: Paint chipping or flaking off
rust or corrosion on the vehicle's body.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the subframe can cause the steering system to fail, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the vehicle makes a loud noise when turning
the steering wheel shakes or vibrates
and the vehicle is hard to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The brakes are spongy
the brakes make a loud noise
the vehicle pulls to one side when braking
and the vehicle is hard to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The misalignment of the vehicle can cause uneven tire wear, reduced traction, and loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
the tires are unevenly worn
and the vehicle is hard to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion and failure of the rear subframe can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle may exhibit symptoms such as a loose or unstable rear end
uneven tire wear
and unusual noises or vibrations while driving. In severe cases
the subframe may break
causing loss of control and accidents.
